            <h3>State-of-the-Art Facilities</h3>
            <p>Aatura Hospital's General Surgery Department is equipped with state-of-the-art facilities, including advanced operating rooms, surgical suites, and intensive care units, to support a wide range of surgical procedures and patient care needs. Our hospital features cutting-edge surgical technology, diagnostic imaging, and perioperative services to ensure the highest standards of safety, efficiency, and quality in surgical care.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content3">
        <div class="cl">
            <h3>Expert Surgical Team</h3>
            <p>Our General Surgery Department is staffed by a team of highly skilled and experienced surgeons, anesthesiologists, nurses, and support staff dedicated to providing exceptional surgical care to our patients. Our surgeons are board-certified and trained in the latest surgical techniques and advancements, delivering personalized and compassionate care to meet the unique needs of each patient.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

    <div class="content4">
