            <h3>Contact Us</h3>
            <p>If you require surgical treatment or have questions about our general surgical services, please contact our General Surgery Department. Our team is here to provide expert evaluation, treatment, and support to address your surgical needs and improve your health and well-being.</p>
        </div>
    </div>

